>\n<p>先参考一个 YouTube 视频<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HTHH5xvQZyc\" rel=\"nofollow\">How to Cut, Trim, &amp; Shape Your Own Hair: Medium Length Men's Hair</a>，再买好装备，总结三个关键点：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>对于新手一定要有限位梳子，最好是有左右俩边的坡度限位</li>\n<li>第二点非常重要，一定不能一次性理太短，不然没法修🤣</li>\n<li>没有第三点，总之非常简单，给生活带来了极大便利</li>\n</ol>\n", "last_modified": 1718427587, "replies": 81, "id": 1049738}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/301a/d0e3/834_large.png?m=1584400459", "name": "xiaomi", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/301a/d0e3/834_normal.png?m=1584400459", "title": "小米", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/xiaomi", "topics": 1021, "footer": "", "header": "关于小米公司出品的各种智能硬件的使用讨论", "title_alternative": "Xiaomi", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/301a/d0e3/834_mini.png?m=1584400459", "stars": 385, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 834, "parent_node_name": "android"}, "member": {"id": 517388, "username": "docxs", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/docxs", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ebdada4320a2b38bf7a6a75abf82427d?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ebdada4320a2b38bf7a6a75abf82427d?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ebdada4320a2b38bf7a6a75abf82427d?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1605322671, "last_modified": 1662124137}, "last_reply_by": "EndlessMemory", "last_touched": 1718504597, "title": "小米空调咋这么费电，兄弟们有一样的吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1049781", "created": 1718440458, "deleted": 0, "content": "买了个 1.5P N1A1 ，客服给的数据 0.31 度/H ，我这开了 16.5H ，用了 14 度，空调伴侣统计的。差的也太多了吧，这还不到最热的时候。。。无语", "content_rendered": "<p>买了个 1.5P N1A1 ，客服给的数据 0.31 度/H ，我这开了 16.5H ，用了 14 度，空调伴侣统计的。差的也太多了吧，这还不到最热的时候。。。无语</p>\n", "last_modified": 1718440458, "replies": 61, "id": 1049781}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1695370146", "name": "career", "ava