个人可以共同消费.<br />2. 由于一些原因, 某一天 D 有事情, 不能参加中午的聚餐, 所以只有 A, B, C 三个人参加了聚餐, 总共消费 54 元. 此时卡里为 276 元.<br />3. 由于 D 并没有参加这次 54 元的消费, 所以 D 如果继续参加接下来的 4 人聚餐, 会有点 “吃亏”.<br />4. 请问 A, B, C 应该各付给 D 多少钱, 从而抹平这次消费, 且保证之后的 4 人聚餐公平, 即 4 个人所持有的会员卡余额份额保持一致?", "last_modified": 1718476358, "replies": 30, "id": 1049818}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ea5d/2f1c/64_large.png?m=1712640468", "name": "youtube", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ea5d/2f1c/64_normal.png?m=1712640468", "title": "YouTube", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/youtube", "topics": 689, "footer": "", "header": "世界上最大的视频网站，由前 PayPal 员工创建，后来被 Google 收购。一个你绝对不应该错过的信息源。", "title_alternative": "YouTube", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ea5d/2f1c/64_mini.png?m=1712640468", "stars": 875, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 64, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 76837, "username": "busterian", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/busterian", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cca9/2d2a/76837_mini.png?m=1718429559", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cca9/2d2a/76837_normal.png?m=1718429559", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cca9/2d2a/76837_large.png?m=1718429559", "created": 1413089134, "last_modified": 1718429559}, "last_reply_by": "LunarEclipse", "last_touched": 1718469885, "title": "ytb 将在服务器端把 ads 注入到视频内, vu 怎么看", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1049749", "created": 1718429723, "deleted": 0, "content": "![img]( https://i.imgur.com/wC2QaxM.png)", "content_rendered": "![img]( <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wC2QaxM.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wC2QaxM.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a>)", "last_modified": 1718433428, "replies": 28, "id": 1049749}]